RAWALPINDI, Jul 05 (APP):The Indian Army Troops resorted to unprovoked ceasefire violation in Battal Sector along the line of control (LoC) and targeted civil population with mortars and heavy weapons, late last night.
Due to Indian troops firing, a 22 years old civilian got injured whereas the Pakistan Army troops responded effectively to Indian firing, said Inter Services Public Relations (ISPR).
